# early copy is necessary so that the gcc -B options find
# the right startup files when linking shared libgcc.

  rm -f ../.././gcc/$file;		\

  case $file in 					\
    *.a)						\
      /usr/i686-w64-mingw32/bin/ranlib ../.././gcc/$file ;;	\
  esac;							\
done
